subject: p12530259
Findings: In comparison with study of earlier in this date, there is little interval change. Substantial opacification of the left hemithorax persists with the right lung being essentially clear. No appreciable pneumothorax. Gas within soft tissues is seen in the supraclavicular level on the left. IJ catheter is unchanged.
